Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.75,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.00,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}变得像样多了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.66,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.91,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.62,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是新来的那些人的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:44.75,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是什么声音？
